OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fbright end to the day with plenty of
OL,7,Fclear skies. Low risk of some patchy
OL,8,Fcloud Skies remaining largely clear
OL,9,Falthough some patchy cloud may push in
OL,10,Ffrom the west near dawn. Remaining
OL,11,Fwarm overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,14,Ffor much of the region, although some
OL,15,Fcloud and a few spots of rain may move
OL,16,Finto Cumbria during the afternoon.
OL,17,FFeeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
